extendedInfo.description: The #1 thrilling running experience now comes to the underworld! Begin your exhilarating adventure now and see how far you can run!In this fast paced vampire rushing game, it's your job to guide the vampire hero through an impossible underworld of monsters, werewolves, zombies and dark priests. This fast paced and frustratingly addictive adventure guarantees you many long hours of fun! With great controls, a truly standout presentation, and plenty of useful power-ups to chase, itâs also highly entertaining.How to Play:- Tap the screen to jump from floor to ceiling or vice versa, knocking down enemies while in the air- Get a boost of speed and power using pickups of Cerberus, Bat or Death KnightGame Features:- BEAUTIFUL! Amazing graphics and original sound effects- SMOOTH! Intuitive touch controls and tutorial- FUN! Critically acclaimed game play in your hands

reviews.title: OK
reviews.comment: I didn\'t expect much from this but the game turned out to be alright after all. It\'s like Jetpack Joyride with better scenery, so it\'s not really original. The graphics are great and very smooth, but the game has to be played on full brightness otherwise you can\'t see the obstacles. There\'s a lot of grammar mistakes in the store as well, but I found the game enjoyable and I will keep playing it. I prefer this from JJ because of the small storage consumption and the smoothness, can\'t wait for some updates.
